Fixed sync-labels.yml workflow - 3 bugs resolved
## Summary
Workflow had empty matrix array causing validation errors and js-yaml module resolution issues.

## Changes Made
- Commented out unused batch-sync job with empty `repository: []` matrix
- Added explicit `js-yaml@4.1.0` global install
- Used `$(npm root -g)` for dynamic NODE_PATH resolution

## Related Files
- .github/workflows/sync-labels.yml:86-113, 207-240

